The,StorageMadeEasy,Cloud,Data,API,enables,users,to,use,one,API,to,work,with,over,public,and,private,storage,and,information,Clouds,The,API,aims,to,solve,the,key,issue,of,unifying,cloud,information,across,different,cloud,services,Functionality,includes,accessing,control,permissions,file,locking,event,auditing,and,can,be,used,natively,as,a,Cloud,drive,on,any,desktop,or,mobile,device,It,is,RESTful,with,responses,in,XML,supporting,all,kinds,of,authentication,protocols,from,differing,Cloud,services